```
# Shell script related ignores (if any temporary files are generated during execution)
*.tmp
*.log
*.out

# Environment files that might be used in scripts
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# Backup files
*~
*.bak
*.backup

# Compressed archives (commonly created by scripts)
*.zip
*.gz
*.tar
*.tgz
*.bz2
*.xz
*.7z
*.rar
*.zst

# System files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Processed data/output that might be generated by the scripts
*log/
*output/
*results/
*data/

```